{"title":"如何代码高亮","uid":"f24c5ec03771d4cbbc3ad769a5db328c","slug":"代码高亮","date":"2021-07-17T13:51:39.000Z","updated":"2021-08-10T15:57:35.566Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/代码高亮.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/05/30/4kbizhi/2.jpg","content":"<h1 id=\"matery主题不知什么原因，代码显示如下：\"><a href=\"#matery主题不知什么原因，代码显示如下：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"matery主题不知什么原因，代码显示如下：\"></a><center>matery主题不知什么原因，代码显示如下：</h1><p><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/07/17/daimagaoliang/1.png\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/07/17/daimagaoliang/0.png\"><br><img src=\"https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/sky20681/sky20681/2021/07/17/daimagaoliang/2.png\"></p>\n<p>原来是没有卸载原<code>hexo</code>自带的高亮和禁用主题的高亮……</p>\n<h2 id=\"修改如下-：\"><a href=\"#修改如下-：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"修改如下 ：\"></a><center>修改如下 ：</h2><p>如果你的博客中曾经安装过 <code>hexo-prism-plugin</code> 的插件，那么你须要执行 <code>npm uninstall hexo-prism-plugin</code> 来卸载掉它，否则生成的代码中会有<code>&amp;#123; 和 &amp;#125;</code>的转义字符。</p>\n<p>然后，修改 Hexo 根目录下 <code>_config.yml </code>文件中 <code>highlight.enable</code> 的值为 <code>false，</code>并将 <code>prismjs.enable</code> 的值设置为<code> true，</code>主要配置如下：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-css\" data-language=\"css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">highlight</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">enable</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> false\n  <span class=\"token property\">line_number</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> true\n  <span class=\"token property\">auto_detect</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> false\n  <span class=\"token property\">tab_replace</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">wrap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> true\n  <span class=\"token property\">hljs</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> false\n<span class=\"token property\">prismjs</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">enable</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> true\n  <span class=\"token property\">preprocess</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> true\n  <span class=\"token property\">line_number</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> true\n  <span class=\"token property\">tab_replace</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<p>Matery主题中默认的 <code>prismjs </code>主题是 <code>Tomorrow Night，</code>如果你想定制自己的主题，可以前往 <a href=\"https://prismjs.com/download.html#themes=prism-funky&languages=markup+css+clike+javascript\">prismjs</a> 下载页面 定制下载自己喜欢的主题 <code>css</code> 文件，然后将此<code> css</code> 主题文件取名为<code> prism.css，</code>替换掉 <code>hexo-theme-matery</code> 主题文件夹中的 <code>source/libs/prism/prism.css </code>文件即可。</p>\n<p>然后到主题配置下启用代码复制/折叠/收缩等，如下：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-css\" data-language=\"css\"><code class=\"language-css\"># 代码块相关\n<span class=\"token property\">code</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">lang</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> false # 代码块是否显示名称\n  <span class=\"token property\">copy</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> true # 代码块是否可复制\n  <span class=\"token property\">shrink</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> true # 代码块是否可以收缩\n  <span class=\"token property\">break</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> true # 代码是否折行<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n","text":"matery主题不知什么原因，代码显示如下：